# Cloudflare Pages security headers for the FluxTube dashboard PWA.
#
# Format reference: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
#
# Baseline matches site/public/_headers (A+ on securityheaders.com) with
# adjustments for the dashboard's interactive surface:
#
#   - `form-action 'self'` instead of `'none'` — the OAuth-begin
#     hyperlink is a same-origin GET, but if any future flow adds a
#     POST form the `'self'` value keeps it working.
#   - `connect-src 'self'` — the Preact islands hit /api/*, all
#     same-origin. Cloudflare Pages proxies to the dashboard Worker
#     via Service Binding, so no cross-origin fetch is required.
#   - No CSP nonces on inline styles/scripts. Astro emits inline style
#     attributes via `define:vars` and small IIFEs; nonce-injection
#     would add build complexity for a private-audience surface with
#     no user-controlled markup. `'unsafe-inline'` is the pragmatic
#     choice — same reasoning as the marketing site.
#   - `Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp` still safe: the
#     only cross-origin fetches are Google Fonts, which already emit
#     the correct CORP/CORS headers upstream.
#   - `X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow` — dashboard is private per
#     tenant; robots.txt disallow is not enough (some crawlers ignore
#     it), the response header is authoritative.
#
# Defaults Pages already sets (don't redeclare):
#   - x-content-type-options: nosniff
#   - referrer-policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
#   - HTTP → HTTPS 301 redirect

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' data:; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; connect-src 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; upgrade-insecure-requests
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: same-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Permissions-Policy: accelerometer=(), camera=(), geolocation=(), gyroscope=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=(), interest-cohort=()
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow
